reviewText: I bought this DVD for the family to enjoy and we did. Very good!
Some really great romantic movies. I bought it for "Sleepless In Seattle" and hadn't seen the other two movies but they are both as good as Sleepless. I am so happy I decided to try them.
I have always been very fond of the lead actors.  The story line makes a wonderful theme for 2 good personalities to show the world what is really important for a happy productive life.
